edu.xtec.util

Class CompoundObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.xtec.util.CompoundObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    GroupData, UserData

    public class CompoundObject
extends Object
implements Serializable
    This class encapsulates three fields: a text identifier, a label and an icon. The icon is always an external resource, accessible through an URL.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Francesc Busquets (fbusquets@xtec.cat)
